<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٣٧٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7213">يُوسُفُ بْنُ عِيسَى: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5879">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ فُضَيْلٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5117">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2511">أَبِي حَازِمٍ، </a>عَنْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٦٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«مَا شَبِعَ آلُ مُحَمَّدٍ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> مِنْ طَعَامٍ ثَلَاثَةَ أَيَّامٍ حَتَّى قُبِضَ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>